= Overview =

Currently JSS is using a very basic custom logging framework:

* https://github.com/dogtagpki/jss/blob/master/org/mozilla/jss/util/Debug_debug.jnot
* https://github.com/dogtagpki/jss/blob/master/org/mozilla/jss/util/Debug_ship.jnot

JSS should be modified to use a more commonly used logging framework such as  SLF4J.

